{
  "stem": "13655.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very high blood pressure, and she couldn't walk, but my daughter took her-- my sister took her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took her to Biala.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was the last one, with a few from my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had in mind-- when I left, this was already by the evening, by sunset.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt so bad, and I cursed at all the world, and with a curse on my [? town. ?] Why you doing?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why you have to leave it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just go on like a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had in mind, me, and my cousin [INAUDIBLE], and my friend Chaim Goldberg, not to go to Biala.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll go about 10 miles, 10 kilometers in the train, and we'll go out in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we came to that particular place to go out, but nobody was watching us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, where are you going to go, Louis?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look who is going there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew it already, because it is going to disband, because the neighborhood-- the neighborhood, [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lodz, ?] it was cleaned up already with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I said to myself, where do you go?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have all of your family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they're not going to be alive, what do you need?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You don't [INAUDIBLE] your life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I canceled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I backed out from that plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went into Biala.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, to Biala.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, I canceled my plan to go to the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot leave my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is my blood and flesh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to go with them, wherever they'll be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We arrived Thursday night to Biala, in the evening already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Judenrats from there took us here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had an uncle there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
